name: Dueter
description: Music On Metaverse! Dueter will be the founder of a new world of music, in the not too distant future we will take you to the dream world of Metaverse and bring world day concerts of different artists to your room, get ready for this with any possibility and any budget.The project will focus on music with the Metavars roadmap and NFTs on the work of music artists around the world.
